Mr. Weston.text: I suppose you have heard of the handsome letter Mr. Frank Churchill has written to Mrs. Weston ? I understand it was a very handsome letter , indeed . Mr. Woodhouse told me of it . Mr. Woodhouse saw the letter , and he says he never saw such a handsome letter in his life . "

Mr. Woodhouse.text: Ah , poor Miss Taylor ! She would be very glad to stay . "
